name: Narroway
goal: Stimulate the sustainable growth of organisations, companies and brands by increasing their perceived value and degree of irreplaceability. Through giving insight into how the biotic laws apply to their specific situation, assess the blockages and deficiencies slowing their growth and developing the roadmap that will allow them to overcome these. Effectively and measurably.
interests: Agriculture and Rural Development, Climate Action, Communication, Consumer Affairs, Culture, Development, Enterprise, Environment, External Relations, Fisheries and Aquaculture, Food Safety, Humanitarian Aid, Public Health, Research and Technology
